ro%20review%3A%20An%20affordable%20standing%20desk%20with%20a%20massive%20weight%20capacity%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Business%20Insider%20may%20earn%20an%20affiliate%20commission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-reviews-expertise-in-product-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22side%20by%20side%20of%20author%20working%20at%20a%20standing%20desk%20and%20a%20front%20on%20view%20of%20the%20flexispot%20standing%20desk%20with%20a%20laptop%20on%20top%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671177e7fd8ede6c99e395c3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Flexispot%20E7%20Pro%20standing%20desk%20is%20a%20workhorse.%20It's%20stable%20at%20any%20height%20and%20smoothly%20adjusts%20throughout%20the%20day.%20It%20can%20also%20lift%20and%20support%20up%20to%20440%20pounds%20of%20gear.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20working%20from%20home%20for%20nearly%2010%20years%20and%20in%20that%20time%2C%20I've%20had%20a%20few%20different%20desks%20%E2%80%94%20some%20that%20I%20made%20and%20others%20that%20I%20thrifted.%20All%20the%20desks%20that%20I've%20used%20required%20me%20to%20sit%2C%20and%20I%20know%20how%20unhealthy%20sitting%20can%20be.%20Even%20before%20I%20worked%20from%20home%2C%20I'd%20heard%20about%20the%20benefits%20of%20standing%20desks%2C%20but%20I%20never%20thought%20to%20get%20one%20myself.%20I%20was%20ecstatic%20to%20see%20what%20the%20fuss%20was%20about%20with%20the%20Flexispot%20E7%20Pro%20Standing%20Desk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Flexispot%20E7%20Pro%20Standing%20Desk%20is%20minimalist%20in%20style%20but%20offers%20an%20easy-to-use%20touch%20control%20panel%20that%20raises%20and%20lowers%20the%20desktop%20to%20your%20preferred%20standing%20or%20sitting%20height.%20I%20put%20the%20desk%20together%20myself%20and%20tested%20it%20over%20two%20weeks%20to%20determine%20how%20well%20it%20suited%20my%20work%20life.%20Keep%20reading%20to%20see%20why%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-standing-desk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20standing%20desks%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229750067f-69b0-4852-b536-6b0b2320a502%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Design%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDesign%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20view%20of%20a%20flexispot%20standing%20desk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67117fcbfd8ede6c99e39888%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20E7%20Pro%20is%20minimalist%20in%20appearance%2C%20but%20customizable%20to%20your%20needs%2C%20with%20the%20option%20for%20add-ons.%20%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEverybody's%20work%20requirements%20are%20different%2C%20so%20it's%20nice%20to%20see%20that%20Flexispot%20lets%20you%20customize%20the%20E7%20Pro%20Standing%20Desk%20to%20your%20exact%20needs.%20The%20first%20step%20I%20took%20in%20ordering%20this%20desk%20was%20choosing%20a%20desktop%20material.%20I%20chose%20the%20blonde%20bamboo%20option%20as%20I%20thought%20it%20would%20fit%20nicely%20with%20my%20home%20d%C3%A9cor.%20Other%20options%20include%20solid%20wood%2C%20chipboard%2C%20and%20solid%20wood%20texture%20(a%20board%20made%20of%20poplar%20and%20eucalyptus%20and%20then%20wrapped%20in%20what%20looks%20like%20wood-textured%20material).%20There%20is%20also%20an%20Ergo%20Series%20desktop%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Bsoft%2C%20skin%20touch%20panels%26quot%3B%20that%20are%20%26quot%3Bslip%20resistant%20and%20durable.%26quot%3B%20It's%20not%20exactly%20clear%20what%20they're%20made%20of.%20You%20can%20also%20opt%20to%20purchase%20just%20the%20frame%20and%20use%20your%20own%20tabletop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20there%2C%20customers%20choose%20whether%20they%20want%20the%20desktop%20curved%20or%20straight.%20In%20terms%20of%20size%2C%20I%20ordered%20a%2048%20by%2024%20inch%20desktop.%20In%20person%2C%20the%20desk%20looks%20like%20a%20typical-sized%20desk%20that%20can%20fit%20a%20single%20monitor.%20Desk%20sizes%20go%20up%20to%2078%20by%2030%20inches%2C%20which%20is%20something%20to%20consider%20if%20you%20have%20multiple%20monitors%20and%20an%20office%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20close%20up%20of%20the%20digital%20control%20panel%20on%20a%20standing%20desk%20reading%2042.9%20inches%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67117fb7a0a0cc14f221de79%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20control%20panel%20displays%20the%20desk's%20exact%20height%2C%20allows%20you%20to%20make%20four%20pre-sets%2C%20and%20has%20a%20USB%20port%20to%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20charge%20your%20phone.%20%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20I%20ordered%20the%20E7%20Pro%2C%20it%20was%20outfitted%20with%20a%20solid%20carbon%20steel%20base%20C-Frame%2C%20which%20I%20ordered%20in%20white.%20(If%20you%20order%20the%20E7%20version%20of%20this%20desk%2C%20it%20will%20come%20with%20a%20T-frame).%20The%20C-frame's%20thicker%20leg%20columns%20are%20set%20on%20the%20back%20of%20the%20base%2C%20providing%20extra%20under-desk%20space.%20The%20legs%20and%20the%20dual%20motor%2C%20which%20is%20under%20the%20desktop%20and%20has%20had%2030%2C000-plus%20lift%20tests%2C%20have%20the%20capability%20to%20bear%20440%20pounds.%20For%20reference%2C%20the%20dual%20motor%20looks%20like%20a%20large%20rectangular%20battery%20with%20cords%20that%20connect%20to%20the%20keypad%2C%20the%20legs%2C%20and%20an%20outlet.%20The%20desk%20must%20be%20plugged%20into%20an%20outlet%20for%20the%20motor%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20its%20minimalistic%20design%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20outfit%20the%20desk%20with%20organization%20and%20storage%20elements.%20Additional%20accessories%20for%20this%20desk%2C%20such%20as%20caster%20wheels%2C%20chairs%2C%20power%20strips%2C%20docking%20stations%2C%20and%20some%20cable%20management%20tools%2C%20can%20be%20added%20to%20your%20Flexispot%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ce65ea72-dfaa-4a00-a625-77fce1c42269%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Setup%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESetup%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22three%20flexispot%20boxes%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67117fa8a0a0cc14f221de5e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFlexispot%20ships%20quickly%2C%20but%20the%20packages%20were%20delivered%20in%20a%20few%20boxes%20over%20two%20days.%20%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20packaging%20was%20a%20little%20heavy%2C%20I%20could%20set%20this%20desk%20up%20on%20my%20own.%20The%20desk%20arrived%20in%20a%20few%20boxes%20over%20two%20days.%20When%20I%20began%20assembling%20the%20desk%2C%20I%20discovered%20that%20the%20instructions%20were%20a%20little%20lacking.%20Like%20most%20instruction%20manuals%2C%20it%20had%20pictures%20and%20some%20text%2C%20but%20at%20times%2C%20I%20became%20confused%20on%20how%20to%20exactly%20proceed.%20(I%20should%20mention%20that%20I'm%20a%20practiced%20reviewer%20who%20has%20assembled%20far%20more%20technical%20things%20like%20grills%20and%20yard%20tools.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22parts%20of%20a%20desk%20assembled%20on%20the%20floor%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6711800101ea6d83dee20813%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere%20were%20lots%20of%20small%20parts%20to%20assemble%2C%20but%20everything%20was%20included.%20%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20there%20were%20some%20holes%20that%20were%20pre%20cut%20into%20the%20bamboo%2C%20but%20the%20instructions%20made%20no%20mention%20of%20aligning%20the%20beam%20or%20the%20frame%20to%20those%20holes.%20(Even%20when%20I%20tried%20to%20align%20the%20beam%20to%20the%20holes%2C%20it%20didn't%20really%20work.)%20I%20had%20some%20trouble%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20adjust%20the%20length%20of%20the%20frame.%20While%20the%20instructions%20say%20that%20the%20distance%20from%20the%20support%20plate%20to%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20table%20should%20not%20exceed%207.87%20inches%2C%20the%20way%20that%20it's%20shown%20in%20the%20instructions%20is%20confusing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20progress%20of%20a%20desk%20being%20assembled%20together%2C%20revealing%20the%20under%20carriage%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67117f8401ea6d83dee207c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere%20were%20some%20hiccups%20during%20assembly%2C%20aligning%20everything%20and%20getting%20screws%20in%20place.%20%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20to%20mention%2C%20it%20was%20difficult%20to%20screw%20in%20the%20screws%20with%20the%20provided%20screwdriver.%20If%20you%20have%20a%20drill%2C%20I%20suggest%20using%20it%2C%20as%20there%20were%20times%20when%20the%20screwdriver%20that%20Flexispot%20provided%20came%20close%20to%20stripping%20the%20screws.%20Other%20times%2C%20I%20was%20unable%20to%20get%20the%20screw%20all%20the%20way%20into%20the%20desktop%20as%20the%20screws%20are%20very%20thick%20and%20the%20bamboo%20is%20hard%20to%20push%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstalling%20the%20control%20panel%20was%20far%20easier%20than%20I%20expected.%20It%20took%20me%20seconds%20to%20connect%20it%20and%20set%20up%20my%20preferred%20standing%20and%20sitting%20heights.%20Then%2C%20I%20could%20push%20just%20one%20button%20and%20watch%20the%20desk%20lift%20and%20lower%20to%20my%20exact%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226f55dabc-4d25-4dc2-995e-427014aae431%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Living%20with%20the%20desk%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELiving%20with%20the%20desk%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20woman%20working%20at%20a%20standing%20desk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67117f78a0a0cc14f221de4f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20E7%20Pro%20didn't%20wobble%20or%20sway%20when%20leaning%20on%20it%20while%20standing.%20%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20the%20Flexispot%20E7%20Pro%20Standing%20Desk%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%20was%20easy%20enough.%20I%20found%20myself%20switching%20between%20sitting%20and%20standing%20throughout%20the%20day.%20Because%20I%20had%20preset%20my%20standing%20and%20sitting%20positions%2C%20moving%20between%20the%20two%20positions%20was%20no%20problem%20at%20all.%20The%20desk%20felt%20stable%20whether%20it%20was%20raised%20or%20lowered%2C%20so%20much%20so%20that%20when%20I%20leaned%20against%20it%20while%20standing%2C%20it%20didn't%20wobble%20or%20move%20under%20my%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20assembling%20the%20desk%2C%20I%20set%20up%20my%20laptop%2C%20keyboard%2C%20and%20mouse.%20I%20don't%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20equipment%20and%2C%20thus%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20cords%2C%20so%20I%20didn't%20utilize%20the%20cable%20tray%20organizer.%20I%20liked%20that%20the%20control%20panel%20had%20a%20USB%20port%2C%20making%20charging%20my%20phone%20while%20I%20worked%20much%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2232da3236-81ec-4fcc-9d03-adf2dfada39d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpeed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Flexispot%20E7%20Pro%20Standing%20Desk%20lifts%20and%20lowers%20quite%20smoothly.%20The%20desk%20rose%20from%2025%20inches%20to%2050.6%20inches%20in%2017.5%20seconds%2C%20which%20is%20about%202%20inches%20per%20second.%20Most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20you'll%20only%20be%20lifting%20the%20desk%20from%20a%20sitting%20to%20a%20standing%20height%2C%20which%20should%20take%20about%207.5%20seconds%20%E2%80%94%20just%20as%20it%20did%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20the%20speed%2C%20the%20motor%20has%20a%2061%20dB%20sound%20rating.%20This%20is%20slightly%20louder%20than%20others%20on%20the%20market%2C%20but%20in%20the%20grand%20scheme%20of%20things%2C%20it's%20not%20loud%20or%20bothersome%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225b4448d5-7729-4a76-aa21-f1a0ac763fbb%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%20capacity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Flexispot%20E7%20Pro%20Standing%20Desk%20has%20a%20weight%20capacity%20of%20440%20lbs.%20To%20test%20this%20out%2C%20I%20sat%20atop%20the%20desk%20and%20lifted%20it%20up%20and%20then%20down.%20For%20reference%2C%20I%20weigh%20175%20lbs.%20The%20motor%20worked%20perfectly%20fine%20during%20this%20test.%20Most%20people's%20work%20equipment%20will%20not%20weigh%20440%20lbs.%20or%20even%20175%20lbs.%2C%20but%20if%20yours%20happens%20to%2C%20this%20desk%20can%20surely%20handle%20the%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e0379c57-f6b5-4b2f-9f5a-a54b05d15f85%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20relation%20to%20the%20desk%20itself%2C%20there%20aren't%20many%20cons.%20The%20only%20drawback%20that%20I%20discovered%20in%20my%20use%20of%20the%20Flexispot%20E7%20Pro%20was%20in%20the%20assembly%20process.%20The%20instruction%20manual%20wasn't%20as%20easy%20to%20understand%20as%20I%20would%20have%20liked%2C%20and%20the%20provided%20screws%20were%20quite%20difficul