C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20a%20substantial%20percentage%20of%20the%2021%20million%20bitcoin%20that%20will%20ever%20exist%2C%20and%20such%20a%20massive%20sale%20was%20long%20feared%20as%20a%20bearish%20event%20for%20the%20token.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Satoshi%20did%20not%20leave%20proper%20instructions%20to%20transfer%20the%20assets%20upon%20their%20death%2C%20then%20the%20fixed%20supply%20of%2021%20million%20bitcoins%20is%20probably%20closer%20to%2020%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESean%20Farrell%2C%20head%20of%20digital%20assets%20strategy%20at%20Fundstrat%2C%20highlighted%20this%20dynamic%20in%20a%20note%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20slight%20upside%20risk%20if%20they%20identify%20someone%20who%20is%20deceased%2C%20as%20this%20would%20effectively%20'burn'%20Satoshi's%20supply%20for%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20Farrell%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBitcoin's%20true%20float%20is%20undoubtedly%20below%2021%20million%2C%26quot%3B%20Farrell%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20something%20that%20we%20all%20know%20to%20be%20true%20but%20is%20nearly%20impossible%20to%20verify.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20also%20because%20losing%20bitcoin%20is%20relatively%20easy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjames-howells-threw-away-bitcoin-dump-masterplan-get-back-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeven%20when%20you're%20still%20alive.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELost%20bitcoin%20essentially%20%26quot%3Bburns%26quot%3B%20it%2C%20decreasing%20the%20amount%20available%20for%20investors%20to%20purchase%20and%20reinforcing%20a%20basic%20economic%20principle%3A%20less%20supply%20means%20higher%20prices%20with%20constant%20or%20increasing%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFarrell%20estimates%20that%20about%201.5%20million%20bitcoins%2C%20or%20about%207.5%25%20of%20the%20total%20supply%2C%20could%20be%20deemed%20%26quot%3Bprobably%20lost%26quot%3B%20because%20they%20haven't%20moved%20since%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20first%20bitcoin%20exchange%20in%202010%2C%20about%20one%20year%20after%20bitcoin%20was%20created.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newyorker.com%2Fmagazine%2F2021%2F12%2F13%2Fhalf-a-billion-in-bitcoin-lost-in-the-dump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20story%20in%20The%20New%20Yorker%20in%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%20profiled%20a%20man%20in%20Wales%20who%20lost%20a%20trove%20of%20bitcoin%20that%2C%20at%20that%20time%2C%20was%20worth%20around%20%24500%20million%20when%20he%20accidentally%20threw%20a%20hard%20drive%20containing%20his%20bitcoin%20stash%20in%20the%20dump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20probably%20only%20with%20the%20passage%20of%20time%20that%20we%20can%20get%20a%20sense%20for%20just%20how%20much%20of%20the%20bitcoin%20supply%20has%20been%20lost%2C%26quot%3B%20Farrell%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESophisticated%20investors%20who%20own%20a%20large%20amount%20of%20bitcoin%20often%20store%20the%20cryptocurrency%20on%20encrypted%20cold%20wallets%20to%20protect%20against%20hacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20these%20cases%2C%20that%20means%20the%20bitcoin%20is%20not%20held%20on%20an%20exchange%20like%20Coinbase%2C%20which%20has%20a%20recovery%20process%20for%20family%20members%20of%20deceased%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%2C%20it's%20typically%20held%20on%20a%20physical%20USB%20drive%20that%20could%20look%20meaningless%20to%20an%20unassuming%20eye%20and%20get%20easily%20lost%20or%20looked%20over%20in%20the%20shuffle%20of%20cleaning%20up%20an%20estate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBitcoin's%20decentralized%20nature%20means%20no%20bank%20or%20authority%20can%20access%20or%20recover%20the%20assets%20without%20the%20private%20key%20to%20the%20wallet%20or%20hard%20drive.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnlike%20traditional%20financial%20accounts%2C%20there%20is%20no%20institution%20to%20contact%20to%20recover%20your%20cryptocurrency.%20If%20no%20one%20has%20your%20private%20key%2C%20the%20funds%20will%20be%20locked%20permanently%2C%26quot%3B%20Wealthica%20CEO