20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20use%20a%20scalpel%20for%20a%20job%20a%20hammer%20can%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20speaking%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20because%20of%20his%20ongoing%20work%20with%20the%20government%2C%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Naval%20Special%20Warfare%20Development%20Group%20(DEVGRU)%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20SEAL%20Team%206%2C%20is%20the%20Navy's%20top-tier%20special%20operations%20outfit.%20Alongside%20the%20Army's%20Delta%20Force%2C%20DEVGRU%20is%20the%20go-to%20special%20missions%20unit%20for%20counterterrorism%20and%20hostage%20rescue%20operations%20anytime%20and%20anywhere.%20The%20unit%20famously%20rescued%20Maersk%20Alabama%20container%20ship%20captain%20Richard%20Phillips%20from%20Somali%20pirates%20in%202009%20and%20killed%20Osama%20bin%20Laden%20in%202011.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228256%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Navy%20SEALs%20engaged%20in%20a%20clearing%20operation%20at%20a%20training%20facility.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6712b385fd8ede6c99e4103c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENavy%20SEALs%20engaged%20in%20a%20clearing%20operation.%3Cp%3EU.S.%20Navy%20photo%20by%20Mass%20Communication%20Specialist%202nd%20Class%20Katie%20Cox%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20don't%20understand%20what%20tier%20one%20units%20are%20all%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20former%20frogman%2C%20a%20term%20for%20Navy%20SEALs.%20%26quot%3BThey%20achieve%20another%20level%20of%20proficiency%20in%20certain%20mission%20sets%20so%20that%20they%20can%20excel%20at%20those%20missions.%20They%20aren't%20intended%20to%20go%20after%20every%20mission%20available%2C%20especially%20if%20another%20SOF%20%5Bspecial%20operations%5D%20unit%20is%20more%20suited%20for%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20large-scale%20invasion%20of%20Taiwan%20would%20mainly%20be%20a%20conventional%20fight.%20A%20unit%20like%20the%20Army's%2075th%20Ranger%20Regiment%2C%20the%20premier%20light%20infantry%20special%20operations%20unit%2C%20would%20probably%20be%20much%20more%20useful%20in%20fighting%20back%20Chinese%20invasion%20forces%20on%20Taiwanese%20soil%20than%20a%20small%20group%20of%20SEAL%20Team%206%20assaulters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20DEVGRU%20would%20definitely%20play%20a%20role%20in%20a%20broader%20conflict%20with%20China.%20If%20we're%20talking%20about%20US%20troops%20fighting%20in%20Taiwan%2C%20then%20it%20means%20a%20decision%20to%20go%20to%20war%20with%20China%20over%20Taiwan.%20In%20a%20situation%20like%20that%2C%20DEVGRU%20would%20likely%20go%20after%20strategic%20targets%20to%20enable%20the%20Big%20Navy%20and%20the%20wider%20conventional%20military%20in%20their%20tasks%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20SEAL%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStrategic%20targets%20like%20air%20bases%2C%20ports%2C%20and%20anti-access%2C%20aerial%20denial%20(A2%2FAD)%20installations%2C%20which%20are%20designed%20to%20take%20out%20US%20carrier%20groups%20or%20repel%20air%20operations%2C%20would%20be%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20target%20deck%20for%20US%20special%20operations%20units.%20SEAL%20Team%206%20and%20the%20Army's%20Delta%20Force%20would%20likely%20go%20after%20such%20targets%20to%20limit%20the%20ability%20of%20the%20Chinese%20military%20to%20wage%20war%20and%20support%20an%20invasion%20of%20Taiwan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221421%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Navy%20SEAL%20during%20a%20nighttime%20dive.%20The%20operator's%20head%20is%20visible%20out%20of%20the%20water%20through%20night-vision%20imaging.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6712b56da0a0cc14f2225837%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22916%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Navy%20SEAL%20during%20a%20nighttime%20dive.%3Cp%3EU.S.%20Navy%20photo%20by%20Mass%20Communication%20Specialist%202nd%20Class%20Katie%20Cox%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Chinese%20navy%2C%20particularly%2C%20would%20be%20a%20primary%20target%20as%20it%20would%20be%20Beijing's%20direct%20link%20to%20the%20invasion%20force%20on%20Taiwan.%20SEAL%20Team%206%2C%20alongside%20other%20SEAL%20units%2C%20could%20go%20after%20Chinese%20warships%20and%20logistics%20vessels%20in%20port%20for%20resupply%20and%20use%20stealthy%20maritime%20insertion%20techniques%20to%20place%20limpet%20mines%20on%20ships%20and%20sensory%20equipment%20in%20and%20around%20naval%20facilities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227735ae38-d40d-40a8-ac04-751980652a47%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20small%20community%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20reason%20why%20SEAL%20Team%206%20would%20likely%20have%20a%20much%20more%20limited%20role%20in%20direct%20combat%20on%20Taiwan%20has%20to%20do%20with%20its%20size.%20Although%20official%20numbers%20are%20classified%2C%20it%20is%20believed%20that%20SEAL%20Team%206%20has%20around%20300%20assaulters%2C%20with%20hundreds%20of%20military%20and%20civilian%20support%20personnel.%20As%20such%2C%20commanders%20will%20generally%20only%20use%20the%20unit%20for%20the%20most%20important%20missions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226982%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Navy%20SEAL%20holding%20a%20service%20weapon%20during%20a%20training%20exercise.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6712b61ba0a0cc14f2225894%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224655%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Navy%20SEAL%20during%20a%20visit%2C%20board%2C%20search%2C%20and%20seizure%20training%20operation.%3Cp%3EU.S.%20Navy%20photo%20by%20Mass%20Communication%20Specialist%202nd%20Class%20Katie%20Cox%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20elite%20unit%20took%20a%20heavy%20hit%2013%20years%20ago%20when%20it%20lost%2025%20assaulters%20and%20direct%20support%20troops%20when%20the%20CH-47%20Chinook%20they%20were%20flying%20on%20crashed%20after%20a%20direct%20hit%20by%20a%20Taliban%20fighter%3B%20in%20total%2C%2038%20US%20and%20Afghan%20troops%20were%20killed.%20The%20incident%20was%20the%20deadliest%20day%20in%20the%20history%20of%20US%20special%20operations%20and%20naval%20special%20warfare.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESEAL%20Team%206%20represents%20the%20cream%20of%20the%20crop%20of%20the%20SEAL%20community.%20It%20recruits%20solely%20from%20the%20SEAL%20Teams%2C%20so%20all%20of%20its%20assaulters%20are%20already%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sandboxx.us%2Fnews%2Fthe-navy-seal-teams-two-original-and-little-known-missions%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENavy%20SEALs%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20unit%20has%20four%20assault%20squadrons%2C%20divided%20by%20color%3A%20Blue%2C%20Red%2C%20Gold%2C%20and%20Silver.%20And%20the%20direct%20support%20personnel%20serving%20with%20the%20unit%20will%20often%20have%20passed%2C%20depending%20on%20their%20role%2C%20Green%20Team%2C%20SEAL%20Team%206's%20physically%20and%20technically%20rigorous%20selection%20process.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fseal-team-6-fight-with-china-over-taiwan-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729338421000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6712b81afd8ede6c99e412e5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fseal-team-6-fight-with-china-over-taiwan-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20role%20of%20the%20elite%20unit%20may%20be%20limited%20but%20not%20inconsequential.%20%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20use%20a%20scalpel%20for%20a%20job%20a%20hammer%20can%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20former%20SEAL%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Stavros%20Atlamazog