0my%20rental%20car%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20have%20insurance%20%E2%80%94%20just%20my%20credit%20card%20reimbursement.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGetting%20the%20charges%20reimbursed%20took%20a%20long%20time%2C%20but%20after%20several%20weeks%20I%20was%20fully%20reimbursed.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGetting%20insurance%20through%20the%20rental%20company%20would%20have%20cost%20far%20more.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20our%20last%20night%20in%20Costa%20Rica%2C%20just%2090%20minutes%20before%20our%20flight%20home%2C%20my%20partner%20and%20I%20pulled%20up%20to%20the%20Enterprise%20Rent-A-Car%20at%20the%20San%20Jos%C3%A9%20airport%20with%20a%20huge%20gash%20on%20the%20left%20side%20of%20our%20rental%20car.%20And%20I'd%20declined%20the%20rental%20company's%20collision%20insurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20I%20had%20rental%20car%20insurance%20through%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fchase-freedom-unlimited-review%5C%22%3EChase%20Freedom%3C%2Fa%3E%20credit%20card.%20I'd%20already%20notified%20Enterprise%20of%20the%20accident%20when%20it%20happened%2C%20so%20I%20naively%20assumed%20we%20could%20just%20drop%20off%20the%20car%20and%20rush%20to%20the%20airport%2C%20and%20Enterprise%20would%20contact%20me%20later%20to%20take%20care%20of%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20I%20ended%20up%20in%20the%20Enterprise%20office%20for%2045%20minutes%2C%20drawing%20Kindergarten-level%20sketches%20of%20the%20accident%20and%20writing%20out%20my%20account%20of%20what%20happened.%20They%20told%20me%20I'd%20have%20to%20complete%20all%20the%20documentation%20there%2C%20and%20then%20I'd%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20them%20to%20make%20copies%20for%20me%20to%20send%20to%20my%20insurance.%20They%20told%20me%20I%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20gather%20these%20copies%20by%20phone%20or%20email.%20I%20wish%20I%20had%20gotten%20there%20early%20enough%20to%20make%20sure%20I%20got%20everything%20I%20needed%20for%20insurance%20because%2C%20as%20I%20later%20found%20out%2C%20they%20were%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20always%20use%20my%20credit%20card%20for%20rental%20cars%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20barely%20made%20it%20on%20our%20flight%2C%20and%20as%20we%20took%20off%2C%20I%20felt%20my%20stomach%20drop%20thinking%20about%20how%20I'd%20just%20been%20charged%20%242%2C500%20for%20damages.%20What%20if%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fbest-credit-cards%5C%22%3Ecredit%20card%3C%2Fa%3E%20didn't%20reimburse%20me%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20make%20it%20a%20point%20to%20book%20rental%20cars%20on%20a%20credit%20card%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fauto-insurance%2Fwhat-is-rental-car-insurance%5C%22%3Erental%20car%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%20benefit%20so%20I%20can%20decline%20the%20rental%20car%20company's%20collision%20insurance%20and%20save%20money%20while%20still%20being%20covered.%20Collision%20damage%20waivers%20can%20cost%20%2415%20to%20%2430%20a%20day%2C%20and%20they%20often%20come%20with%20a%20deductible%2C%20which%20is%20how%20much%20you%20have%20to%20pay%20out%20of%20pocket%20before%20the%20insurance%20will%20even%20kick%20in.%20Overall%2C%20they're%20not%20a%20great%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20saved%20%24250%20on%20my%20rental%20car%20reservation%20this%20time%20by%20declining%20the%20collision%20damage%20waiver.%20In%20Costa%20Rica%2C%20you're%20legally%20required%20to%20have%20both%20the%20collision%20waiver%20and%20third-party%20liability%20coverage%20when%20you%20rent%20a%20car%2C%20but%20you%20can%20get%20the%20former%20waived%20by%20showing%20the%20rental%20car%20company%20proof%20of%20coverage.%20I%20called%20Chase%20the%20day%20before%20I%20left%20and%20had%20card%20benefit%20services%20email%20me%20a%20letter%20verifying%20that%20I'm%20covered%20as%20I%20pay%20for%20the%20car%20using%20my%20Chase%20Freedom%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20done%20this%20dozens%20of%20times%20while%20traveling%20abroad%20and%20probably%20saved%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20in%20total%2C%20but%20I've%20never%20had%20to%20actually%20use%20my%20credit%20card's%20rental%20car%20insurance%20%E2%80%94%20until%20this%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20spent%20hours%20trying%20to%20get%20everything%20to%20file%20a%20claim%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20days%20before%20the%20end%20of%20our%20trip%2C%20my%20partner%20and%20I%20were%20stuck%20in%20traffic%20in%20the%20vibrant%20Caribbean%20surf%20town%20of%20Puerto%20Viejo%2C%20just%20blocks%20from%20our%20vacation%20rental.%20The%20streets%20were%20narrow%2C%20and%20while%20I%20was%20stopped%20in%20a%20line%20of%20traffic%20waiting%20to%20cross%20the%20bridge%2C%20a%20guy%20driving%20a%20massive%20delivery%20truck%20tried%20to%20pass%20me%20and%20turn%20where%20there%20wasn't%20room.%20The%20back%20corner%20of%20the%20truck%20scraped%20into%20the%20side%20of%20my%20rental%20car.%20I%20immediately%20put%20the%20car%20in%20park%2C%20hopped%20out%20to%20flag%20him%20down%2C%20and%20let%20him%20know%20he%20hit%20my%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20most%20difficult%20exams%20I%20took%20in%20college%20Spanish%20couldn't%20compare%20to%20the%20way%20the%20next%20three%20hours%20tested%20my%20language%20skills.%20I%20called%20Enterprise%20first%20to%20explain%20what%20happened.%20They%20then%20sent%20me%20on%20a%20wild%20goose%20chase%20to%20find%20traffic%20police%20%E2%80%94%20different%20from%20criminal%20police%20in%20Costa%20Rica%20%E2%80%94%20to%20cite%20the%20incident.%20The%20closest%20traffic%20police%20officer%20was%20three%20hours%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20waited%20with%20the%20delivery%20driver%2C%20Enterprise%20also%20had%20me%20playing%20phone%20tag%20with%20several%20different%20insurance%20agencies%20to%20get%20one%20of%20their%20agents%20to%20come%20out%20and%20document%20the%20incident.%20I%20tried%20my%20best%20in%20a%20second%20language%20to%20understand%20what%20was%20being%20said%2C%20explain%20the%20accident%2C%20and%20make%20sure%20everything%20was%20documented%20accurately%3B%20I%20knew%20I'd%20need%20all%20of%20these%20forms%20to%20file%20a%20claim%20with%20my%20credit%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20missed%20one%20essential%20document%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20got%20home%20from%20Costa%20Rica%2C%20I%20started%20the%20claims%20process%20with%20my%20credit%20card%20immediately%20so%20I%20could%20be%20reimbursed%20for%20the%20%242%2C500%20charge%20before%20my%20credit%20card%20bill%20was%20due.%20I%20needed%20several%20documents%2C%20including%20an%20accident%20report%2C%20the%20rental%20agency's%20statement%20of%20claim%2C%20my%20car%20rental%20agreement%2C%20a%20repair%20estimate%2C%20two%20photographs%20of%20the%20damaged%20vehicle%2C%20and%20my%20billing%20statement%20showing%20that%20the%20entire%20rental%20transaction%20was%20charged%20to%20my%20Chase%20Freedom%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20I'd%20taken%20a%20few%20photos%20and%20a%20document%20from%20the%20police.%20I%20also%20uploaded%20everything%20I%20had%20gotten%20from%20Enterprise.%20However%2C%20I%20had%20rushed%20out%20of%20there%20to%20catch%20my%20flight%20so%20quickly%2C%20I'd%20forgotten%20to%20grab%20a%20final%20rental%20car%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20the%20next%20month%20trying%20to%20track%20it%20down.%20My%20online%20account%20only%20showed%20U.S.%20rental%20agreements.%20It%20was%20hard%20to%20get%20anyone%20to%20answer%20the%20phone%20at%20the%20Costa%20Rican%20Enterprise%20office%20I%20rented%20from%2C%20and%20when%20I%20did%2C%20they%20would%20give%20me%20an%20email%20address%20to%20contact%20that%20didn't%20work.%20I%20called%20the%20U.S.%20Enterprise%20number%20several%20times%20and%20was%20told%20they%20would%20email%20me%20my%20final%20rental%20agreement%2C%20but%20it%20would%20take%20a%20while%20because%20they%20had%20to%20translate%20it.%20After%20the%20third%20try%2C%20I%20finally%20got%20it%20in%20my%20email%20several%20days%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20claim%20was%20still%20being%20processed%20a%20few%20days%20before%20my%20credit%20card%20bill%20was%20due%2C%20so%20I%20called%20Chase%20and%20explained%20the%20situation.%20They%20agreed%20to%20dispute%20the%20charge%20from%20Enterprise%20until%20my%20claim%20was%20processed%20so%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20to%20cover%20it%20in%20the%20meantime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20when%20I%20thought%20I'd%20completed%20everything%2C%20my%20claim%20agent%20called%20to%20say%20they%20still%20needed%20a%20police%20report.%20Apparently%2C%20the%20piece%20of%20paper%20the%20police%20officer%20handed%20me%20was%20a%20citation%2C%20not%20a%20police%20report.%20If%20it%20was%20this%20hard%20to%20get%20ahold%20of%20Enterprise%20in%20Costa%20Rica%2C%20I%20couldn't%20imagine%20how%20I%20would%20get%20ahold%20of%20the%20police%20department%20and%20track%20down%20that%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20weeks%20trying%20to%20contact%20Enterprise%20to%20see%20if%20they%20had%20the%20report%2C%20and%20then%20I%20tried%20my%20claim%20agent%20again%2C%20who%20said%20they%20could%20also%20try%20to%20track%20down%20the%20report.%20A%20week%20later%2C%20I%20got%20an%20email%20saying%20my%20claim%20had%20been%20approved.%20I'm%20not%20sure%20who%20tracked%20down%20that%20police%20report%20%E2%80%94%20if%20anyone%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I'm%20glad%20it%20didn't%20have%20to%20be%20me.%20They%20deposited%20the%20full%20%242%2C500%20into%20my%20bank%20account%20a%20few%20days%20later%2C%20and%20I%20used%20it%20to%20pay%20off%20the%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EGetting%20insurance%20through%20my%20rental%20company%20would%20have%20been%20easy%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20would%20have%20been%20expensive%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20several%20moments%20where%20I%20wished%20I'd%20just%20gotten%20the%20rental%20car%20company's%20insurance%20%E2%80%94%20when%20I%20almost%20missed%20my%20flight%2C%20when%20I%20saw%20the%20receipt%20for%20the%20%242%2C500%20charge%20and%20worried%20I%20wouldn't%20get%20reimbursed%2C%20when%20I%20was%20attempting%20to%20wade%20through%20Costa%20Rican%20bureaucracy%20with%20my%20less-than-perfect%20Spanish%2C%20and%20when%20I%20was%20told%20I'd%20have%20to%20somehow%20track%20down%20a%20random%20cop%20on%20the%20Caribbean%20side%20of%20the%20country%20who%20had%20filed%20my%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20headache%2C%20but%20it%20was%20worth%20it.%20Not%20only%20did%20I%20save%20%24250%20on%20my%20reservation%2C%20but%20I%20saved%20another%20%241%2C000%20I%20would've%20had%20to%20pay%20to%20cover%20the%20deductible%20on%20the%20rental%20car%20company's%20insurance.%20That's%20not%20even%20counting%20all%20the%20money%20I've%20saved%20over%20the%20years%20on%20rental%20cars%20I%20didn't%20damage.%20I'd%20do%20it%20all%20over%20again%2C%20except%20this%20time%20I'd%20show%20up%20to%20the%20airport%20with%20plenty%20of%20time%20to%20gather%20documentation%2C%20and%20I'd%20brush%20up%20on%20insurance%20vocab%20in%20the%20local%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcredit-card-saved-thousands-rental-car-accident-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729337041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F604a25299942cf001865dc19%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcredit-card-saved-thousands-rental-car-accident-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20spent%20hours%20trying%20to%20collect%20the%20documents%20I%20needed%20for%20my%20insurance%20claim%2C%20but%20even%20after%20several%20weeks%20of%20waiting%2C%20I%20don't%20regret%20my%20choice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Elizabeth%20Aldrich)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcredit-card-saved-thousands-rental-car-accident-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Seema%20con