0Soren%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20key%20face%20in%20Jharkhand%20and%20the%20grand%20alliance%20will%20get%20votes%20on%20his%20name%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20sources%2C%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(M-L)%20and%20Marxist%20Coordination%20Committee%20(MMC)%20also%20want%20to%20join%20forces%20with%20the%20JMM%20and%20Congress%20in%20this%20election.%20The%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%2C%20which%20fought%20on%20seven%20seats%20in%20the%20last%20assembly%20polls%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20contest%20fewer%20seats%20this%20time%20and%20agree%20to%20give%20the%20Bagodar%20seat%20to%20CPI%20(M-L)%20and%20Nirsa%20to%20MMC%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Soren's%20announcement%20came%20a%20day%20after%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20revealed%20its%20seat-sharing%20formula%20for%20the%20state.%20BJP%20will%20contest%2068%20seats%2C%20while%20its%20allies%2C%20All%20Jharkhand%20Students%20Union%20(AJSU)%20will%20contest%2010%2C%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20will%20contest%20two%20and%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(LJP)%20will%20contest%20the%20lone%20seat%20of%20Chatra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNDA%20is%20at%20its%20strongest%20in%20Jharkhand%20so%20far.%20It%20has%20never%20been%20in%20history%20that%20four%20parties%20have%20come%20together%20to%20fight%20the%20elections.%20NDA%20allies%20are%20even%20ready%20to%20swap%20their%20seats%20at%20the%20last%20moment%20if%20needed.%20We%20are%20ready%20to%20throw%20the%20corrupt%20government%20off%20the%20seat.%20All%20NDA%20members%20should%20come%20and%20fight%20with%20us.%20Hemant%20Soren's%20government%20is%20the%20most%20corrupt%20in%20the%20state's%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20leader%20Pratul%20Shah%20Deo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20the%20JMM%20won%2030%20of%20the%2081%20seats%2C%20the%20Congress%2016%20and%20the%20RJD%20won%20one%20seat.%20The%20three%20parties%20formed%20a%20coalition%20gov