%20the%20final%20two%20weeks%20before%20the%20Nov.%205%20election.%20Four%20people%20involved%20in%20the%20group's%20outreach%20told%20Reuters%20that%20managers%20warned%20canvassers%20they%20are%20missing%20targets%20and%20needed%20to%20raise%20the%20number%20of%20would-be%20voters%20they%20contact.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlysia%20McMillan%2C%20who%20canvassed%20for%20the%20PAC%20in%20Wisconsin%2C%20said%20field%20organizers%20recently%20told%20campaigners%20there%20they%20weren't%20reaching%20daily%20objectives%20and%20were%20on%20track%20to%20miss%20an%20ultimate%20goal%20of%20contacting%20450%2C000%20voters%20by%20Election%20Day.%20In%20one%20meeting%20with%20canvassers%2C%20recorded%20by%20McMillan%20and%20reviewed%20by%20Reuters%2C%20a%20manager%20warned%20of%20the%20shortfall.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20going%20to%20hit%20450%2C000%2C%20not%20with%20what%20we've%20got%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20manager%20said%20in%20the%20Oct.%208%20meeting.%20It%20isn't%20clear%20how%20many%20knocks%20the%20Wisconsin%20teams%20have%20reached%20so%20far.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMcMillan%2C%20who%20worked%20for%20two%20local%20contractors%20hired%20by%20America%20PAC%20to%20knock%20on%20voter%20doors%2C%20said%20she%20is%20speaking%20out%20because%20she%20is%20concerned%20a%20shortfall%20could%20cost%20the%20former%20president%20a%20victory.%C2%A0%26quot%3BIf%20this%20isn't%20looked%20into%20in%20a%20timely%20manner%2C%20this%20can%20result%20in%20a%20waste%20of%20time%20and%20money%20and%20risk%20President%20Trump%20winning%20the%20election%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMcMillan%20said%20she%20was%20fired%20by%20one%20contractor%2C%20after%20a%20pay%20dispute%2C%20but%20was%20hired%20by%20another%20shortly%20afterward.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20canvassing%20manager%20in%20Arizona%20said%20leaders%20there%20had%20issued%20similar%20warnings.%20Three%20other%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20outreach%20told%20Reuters%20that%20Chris%20Young%2C%20a%20Musk%20aide%20and%20longtime%20Republican%20operative%2C%20had%20recently%20traveled%20to%20Nevada%20to%20audit%20whether%20doorknocking%20tallies%20there%20had%20been%20inflated%20by%20some%20of%20the%20workers%20hired%20by%20contractors.%20Another%20person%20briefed%20on%20the%20matter%20said%20America%20PAC%20was%20struggling%20to%20find%20sufficient%20people%20to%20conduct%20audits%20in%20other%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20person%20close%20to%20America%20PAC's%20operations%20said%20McMillan's%20account%20of%20a%20Wisconsin%20shortfall%20is%20inaccurate%20and%20that%20the%20group%20will%20reach%20its%20goals.%20Senior%20operatives%2C%20the%20person%20added%2C%20routinely%20visit%20field%20offices%20to%20check%20on%20performance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYoung%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmerica%20PAC's%20ongoing%20outreach%20is%20built%20around%20door-to-door%20efforts%20to%20convince%20%26quot%3Blow%20propensity%20voters%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%93%20those%20who%20may%20support%20Trump%2C%20but%20could%20stay%20home%20instead%20of%20voting%20%E2%80%93%20to%20cast%20their%20ballots.%20The%20work%20has%20focused%20on%20battleground%20states%2C%20where%20any%20small%20difference%20in%20voter%20turnout%20could%20clinch%20victory%20for%20Trump%20or%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20the%20Democratic%20candidate%2C%20in%20an%20election%20that%20polls%20continue%20to%20say%20is%20too%20close%20to%20call.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%2C%20ranked%20by%20Forbes%20as%20the%20world's%20richest%20person%2C%20so%20far%20has%20supplied%20at%20least%20%2475%20million%20to%20America%20PAC%2C%20according%20to%20federal%20disclosures%2C%20making%20the%20group%20a%20crucial%20part%20of%20Trump's%20bid%20to%20regain%20the%20White%20House.%20The%20entrepreneur%20behind%20carmaker%20Tesla%20and%20rocket%20and%20satellite%20venture%20SpaceX%20has%20increasingly%20supported%20Republican%20causes.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20mogul%20became%20an%20outspoken%20supporter%20of%20Trump%2C%20who%20has%20said%20if%20elected%20he%20would%20appoint%20Musk%20to%20head%20a%20government%20efficiency%20commission.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Trump%20campaign%20spokesperson%20declined%20to%20comment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20influx%20of%20cash%2C%20some%20of%20America%20PAC's%20outreach%20has%20been%20plagued%20by%20disarray%2C%20the%20people%20familiar%20with%20its%20efforts%20told%20Reuters.%20As%20with%20many%20campaign%20operations%2C%20the%20group%20has%20hired%20contractors%20to%20carry%20out%20grass-roots%20efforts%2C%20relying%20on%20hourly%20workers%20to%20knock%20on%20doors%20and%20speak%20face-to-face%20with%20potential%20voters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20those%20workers%20have%20been%20difficult%20to%20retain.%20Three%20canvassers%2C%20who%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20identified%2C%20told%20Reuters%20the%20work%20isn't%20worth%20the%20pay%2C%20starting%20at%20some%20contractors%20at%20as%20low%20as%20%2420%20per%20hour.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20they%20added%2C%20canvassers%20drive%20long%20distances%20in%20remote%20areas%20and%20don't%20get%20reimbursed%20for%20gasoline.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Nevada%2C%20it%20isn't%20clear%20whether%20Young's%20audit%20has%20concluded%2C%20reached%20any%20findings%20or%20prompted%20any%20change%20in%20America%20PAC's%20outreach.%20Text%20messages%20reviewed%20by%20Reuters%20show%20managers%20at%20one%20Nevada%20contractor%2C%20Lone%20Mountain%20Strategies%2C%20fretting%20because%20they%20had%20to%20fire%20canvassers%20who%20used%20smartphone%20apps%20to%20disguise%20their%20locations%20and%20lie%20about%20their%20doorknocking%20numbers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20auditors%20keep%20catching%20people%20cheating%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20messages%20read.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20fired%20