compassionate%20capture%20methods%2C%20almost%20always%20without%20nets%20or%20ropes.%20They%20usually%20cover%20the%20dog%20with%20a%20blanket%2C%20scoop%20it%20up%20into%20their%20arms%2C%20and%20quickly%20put%20it%20into%20the%20cage.%20Then%20we%20take%20the%20dog%20to%20the%20government%20veterinary%20hospital%20for%20examination%20and%2For%20treatment.%20Once%20the%20vets%20release%20the%20dog%20for%20aftercare%2C%20we%20bring%20it%20to%20our%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328239%2Fanimal-rescue-and-rehabilitation-centres-in-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnimal%20Rescue%20Centre%3C%2Fa%3E%20(ARC)%2C%20where%20we%20follow%20up%20with%20the%20prescribed%20medications%2C%20nutrition%2C%20rest%2C%20and%20safety%2C%20and%20follow-up%20visits%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20if%20necessary%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Deena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-8-1728641224.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Injured%20stray%20dogs%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-8-1728641224.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-8-1728641224-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-8-1728641224-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-8-1728641224-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-8-1728641224-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369896%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20need%20their%20leg%20amputated%20and%20the%20rehab%20is%20for%20healing%20the%20wound.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20further%2C%20Nurzin%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20the%20rescues%20are%20injuries%20from%20road%20accidents.%20Many%20of%20these%20dogs%20have%20broken%20bones%20and%20need%20casts%20and%20rehab%20for%20several%20weeks.%20Some%2C%20however%2C%20need%20to%20get%20their%20leg%20amputated.%20Other%20cases%20include%20dogs%20suffering%20from%20different%20illnesses%2C%20etc.%20Occasionally%20there%20is%20an%20unusual%20rescue%2C%20where%20a%20dog%20is%20trapped%20in%20a%20hole.%20Our%20people%20are%20terrific%20at%20handling%20these%20situations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-7-Dog-care-1728640276.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stray%20dogs%20at%20the%20shelter%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-7-Dog-care-1728640276.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-7-Dog-care-1728640276-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-7-Dog-care-1728640276-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-7-Dog-care-1728640276-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-7-Dog-care-1728640276-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369884%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20approximately%20170%20dogs%20at%20the%20shelter%20but%20this%20number%20changes%20all%20the%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20one%20such%20rescue%20episode%2C%20Deena%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COne%20time%2C%20some%20young%20women%20called%20us%20for%20help.%20A%20mother%20dog%20had%20delivered%20four%20pups%20in%20a%20small%20room%20in%20an%20abandoned%20building.%20She%20nursed%20them%20till%20they%20were%20about%20three%20months%20old%2C%20then%20the%20mother%20was%20out%20one%20day%20and%20someone%20plastered%20over%20the%20entrance%20and%20the%20pups%20were%20trapped%20inside%20alone.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20our%20team%20arrived%2C%20we%20assessed%20the%20problem.%20Finally%2C%20one%20member%20was%20able%20to%20squeeze%20his%20body%20through%20a%20tiny%20window%20into%20the%20room%20and%20hand%20the%20pups%20out%2C%20one%20at%20a%20time.%20We%20took%20them%20to%20ARC%20and%20cared%20for%20them.%20They%20had%20never%20really%20seen%20the%20light%20of%20day%2C%20or%20been%20around%20people%20or%20other%20dogs.%20They%20required%20a%20lot%20of%20attention%20and%20adjustment%2C%20and%20they%20gradually%20became%20normal%20little%20pups.%20Two%20of%20them%20died%20some%20months%20later%20for%20different%20reasons%2C%20and%20two%20of%20them%20are%20living%20just%20fine%20now%20at%20ARC%20more%20than%20a%20year%20later%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENurturing%20trust%20between%20dogs%20and%20humans%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20things%20that%20stands%20out%20about%20this%20particular%20rescue%20shelter%20is%20how%20comfortable%20these%20dogs%20are%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20(human)%20strangers.%20On%20a%20personal%20visit%20to%20the%20shelter%20in%20September%202022%2C%20it%20was%20interesting%20to%20see%20how%20easy%20and%20comfortable%20it%20was%20to%20enter%20the%20dog%20pens.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENurzin%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20not%20the%20only%20one%20who%20has%20remarked%20on%20this%20aspect.%20We%20often%20take%20first-time%20visitors%20right%20inside%20the%20pens%20to%20meet%20the%20dogs.%20Also%2C%20quite%20a%20number%20of%20dogs%20are%20usually%20roaming%20freely%20in%20the%20central%20area%20and%20the%20area%20right%20in%20front%20of%20our%20little%20house.%20It%20is%20amazing%20to%20us%20that%20none%20of%20them%20are%20aggressive%20towards%20people%20and%20except%20for%20a%20few%20shy%20ones%2C%20they%20are%20friendly%20with%20strangers.%20We%20can%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20feel%20that%20they%20feel%20a%20sense%20of%20safety%20with%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-7-Deena-Dog-1728641055.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Caring%20for%20a%20stray%20dog.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-7-Deena-Dog-1728641055.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-7-Deena-Dog-1728641055-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-7-Deena-Dog-1728641055-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-7-Deena-Dog-1728641055-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FSemchan-Welfare-Society-7-Deena-Dog-1728641055-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369894%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENurzin%20Angmo%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20feel%20that%20they%20feel%20a%20sense%20of%20safety%20with%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20d